---
title: Masala Beef, Green Bean & Potato Curry with Garlic Flatbreads & Yoghurt
description: Forget take-away because this curry is popping with delightfully spiced beef strips, green beans and potato chunks soaking up
the coconut sauce. Serve with garlic flatbreads so not a drop is missed. It’s curry any day, every day!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/64b4dd2ed5b28de23e8e9ea3-d2388576.jpeg
